    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine is currently running but exhibits a persistent knock and visible oil leaks, suggesting it needs major mechanical work. The transmission shifts roughly, and the suspension requires immediate attention. Cosmetically, the body has several significant dents and patches of rust, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest time and money into repairs to make this vehicle roadworthy again.",
